The bottom part of Table 1 shows the ablation exper-
iments of TripleNet. Based on PairNet, TripleNet adds 
three modules (i.e., MFS, IC, CAS, and AFS). When adding 
the MFS module, TripleNet outperforms PairNet by 0.1% 
on object detection and 0.4% on semantic segmentation, 
respectively. When adding the MFS and IC modules, 
TripleNet outperforms PairNet by 0.6% on object detection 
and 0.5% on semantic segmentation. When adding all four 
modules, TripleNet has the best detection performance and 
segmentation performance.
